This paper discusses a decentralized oracle for blockchain, which involves security and cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), and algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also introduces a voting game and analyzes its parameters, which falls under game theory and decision making (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
